## [0.2.0] - 2025-11-22
### Added
- Responsive layout improvements for main dashboard.
- Client-side routing and lazy-loaded routes to reduce initial bundle size.
- Basic accessibility enhancements (aria labels, keyboard navigation).
- Internationalization scaffolding (i18n) with default en locale.
- Form validation helpers and reusable UI components.

### Changed
- Updated UI theme and global styles.
- Refactored state management to use centralized store patterns.

### Fixed
- Several minor UI/UX bugs and layout regressions on mobile viewports.

### Security
- Bumped dependency versions to address known vulnerabilities.

---

## [0.1.0] - 2025-10-01
### Added
- Initial front-end implementation for EchoPanda:
    - Core pages (home, projects, settings).
    - Authentication flow (login/logout).
    - API client with typed responses and error handling.
    - Basic unit tests and CI configuration.
- Project scaffolding with build, lint, and format scripts.

### Fixed
- Initial bug fixes following integration tests.

---

